{"tid":1743774,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[binC]李家超：999求助增加 反映市民支持警隊","createTime":"2019-11-21T11:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T11:32:32.000Z","uid":126099,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"90975927b31dca5b0eb69913a3baf8282b0c0671","tid":1743774,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/police-17_seTTU_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpolice-17_seTTU_1200x0.png&h=f927ee78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n保安局副局長李家超今日在立法會保安事務委員會上形容，整體警民關係仍屬「正面」，他又指出，保安局有客觀數字，判斷警民關係、警隊是否仍受市民信任，例如是999緊急求助電話個案數字、警務人員招募等數字，顯示支持警隊的情況有增無減。<br />\n<br />\n李家超續指，<span style=\"color: red;\">999緊急求助電話個案數字、警務人員招募均有上升，反映警方受市民信任，警員是受歡迎的職業</span>，「第一，999 call要求警方提供協助嘅，2014年有230幾萬，需要跟進嘅個案有90幾萬，比2013年上升5%，在招募警務人員方面，即係警隊是否受歡迎行業來計，係網上遞交申請素表格嘅有1542宗，上升9%，招募日親身出來申請的，有1130宗，上升8%。」<br />\n<br />\n他又補充，網上罪行、科技罪行舉報等數字都上升，「市民好樂意向警方舉報。」李家超認定，數字上升，反映市民仍支持警隊工作，「林林總總（數據），都反映市民對警隊的支持存在，比上年（2013年）上升，信任警隊的情況無減。」<br />\n<br />\n民主黨議員涂謹申批評，當局以報案率等數字判斷警民關係的思路「奇怪」，<span style=\"color: gold;\">「保安局咁樣睇警民關係，咁嘅分析好恐怖。」</span><br />\n<br />\n水炮車增加警隊工具箱選擇<br />\n<br />\n另外，李家超回應，購置水炮車是希望處理大型集會時保持示威者和警員的距離，減少身體接觸和受傷的機會。他形容水炮車是讓警方工具箱內有更多工具可選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85-999%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%A9%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0-%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B6%2585-999%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%25A2%259E%25E5%258A%25A0-%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2598%25A0%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%2F&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameKDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=3e55963b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B6%2585-999%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%25A2%259E%25E5%258A%25A0-%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2598%25A0%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%2F&h=e3c86c7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85-999%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%A9%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0-%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A/</a><br />\n<br />\n焗腸係咪覺得721市民瘋狂支持警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ee0b46f889f67c8bb818e58af737a97f17480a","tid":1743774,"uid":126099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:06:03.000Z","msg":"咁嘅思路做焗腸唔怪得香港搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c628eba90858fd898c249bee806d4ecc6c6b596","tid":1743774,"uid":34722,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:07:39.000Z","msg":"點撚樣a, 721 又話D 人濫用999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85014247685512b663bb8a803ce7e970c1c720dc","tid":1743774,"uid":259097,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:08:00.000Z","msg":"叫得多佢比卡超 唔通我地又支持寵物小精靈牙"},{"pid":"cd076e4d6600f5a755f4a6c94b093f081049d7db","tid":1743774,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:09:56.000Z","msg":"戰役過後，痛定思痛，認清現實，重新出發(抗爭五部曲-前言)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742018</a>"},{"pid":"000b9aeb2b2915dddc455b46e958c5c22d9c7a6f","tid":1743774,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:09:59.000Z","msg":"721四個月"},{"pid":"e1d8a882fd119eeb9bffd0dc0dc0e2068d4f3fab","tid":1743774,"uid":65738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:11:34.000Z","msg":"私了個案增加， 證明市民支持私了"},{"pid":"8eafd0aef4381fbb533083bddf19946d0ce41379","tid":1743774,"uid":235152,"